channel.title: How do i get my server online?
channel.description: I can't seem to get my server to go online so other players can enjoy it. I have made a no-ip and ran the no-ip DUC but it still will not go on. I have tried using my own ip instead of the one from no-ip but it still won't go up. I have also looked in the tutorial section but there dosen't seem to be one on how to get your server online for other players. If anyone could try to help me it would be greatly apreciated. (:
